quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  15,32,"O daali: \"Ko an yo Ibuliisa, e ko he…ďu maa a laatodaaki e sujju…ďe …ďen"
  15,33,"O wi'i: \"Mi wonatah sujjanoowo …ďanndinke mo Tagu…óaa immorde e sen∆īayngal, e loopal-…ďalewal …ďowrungal"
  15,34,"O daali: \"Yaltu ton, an on ko a riiwaa…óo"
  15,35,"pellet, kuddi fawike e ma haa √Īalnde njo…ďdi diina"
  15,36,"O wi'i : \"Joomi am, nennitanam haa √Īalnde nde…ďe immintintee"
  15,37,"O daali:\"An,ko a jeyaa…óo e nennitantee…ďe …ďen"
  15,38,haa e √Īalaande happu anndaa…óo
  15,39,"O wi'i: \"Joomi am, sabu ko bewin…óaa mi kon, ma mi cu…óinan …ďe ka leydi, ma mi bewnu …ďe fow ma…ď…ďe"
  15,40,"si wanaa jeyaa…ďe Maa, la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďen e ma…ď…ďe"
  15,41,"O daali: \"Ngol …óoo ko laawol ka Am focciingol"
  15,42,"Pellet, jeyaa…ďe Am …ďen, a alanaa …ďe cemmbe, si wanaa …ďen bew…ďe jokku…ďe ma"
  15,43,Pellet Jahannama on wonii fodoore ma…ď…ďe …ďe fow
  15,44,Hinge mari dame jee…ói…ói; damal kala e majje no mari ge…ďal senndaangal
  15,45,"Pellet, gom…óu…ďe …ďen wonii e aljannaaji e …ďulli"
  15,46,"Naatiree …ói e kisial, ko on hoolii…ďe"
  15,47,"Men …óoofi kala ko woni e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe e konnaagu(cokotaagal): …ďe wonti musi…ó…ďe fewtondir…ďe e dan…óe"
  15,48,"Tampere he…ďataa …ďe ton, …ďe wonah kadi yaltintee …ďe ton"
  15,49,"Yeetito jeyaa…ďe Am …ďen, ko Min woni Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  15,50,"e wonnde lepte Am …óen, ko …óen woni lepte muusu…óe …óen"
  15,51,Yeetito …ďe kadi fii ho…ď…ďe Ibraahiima …ďen
